constraintnote.p:
A function named "if" can be called by binding its
        namespace to a prefix and using the prefixed form:
        "library:if(foo)" instead of "if(foo)".

div3.p:
Terminal symbols that are not used exclusively in 
      /* ws: explicit */ productions
      are of two kinds: delimiting and non-delimiting.

tr.td:
for,
let,
FLWOR,
some, every, 
switch,
typeswitch,
try,
if
